IL","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/xvnLjjkW1h3gzGHbGI1vG62KjyN.jpg","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/mgKLUQQ7vF0XiAuyAW46RPom0Xs.jpg","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/nrxqdnnm5SliinTsOyGXxt2tx5J.jpg","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/vG42HeYtoTFflqwP42wYD7tBuNr.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/dlyDueDvA022io5Oq3Cy6NOA6tv.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/boKibeDo7AADaYmkhOVmyU6QKLf.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-26T04:42:09.199+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":141,"tagline":"Always have an exit.","homepage":"https://www.amazon.com/salp/crime101?hhf","overview":"When an elusive thief whose high-stakes heists unfold along the iconic 101 freeway in Los Angeles eyes the score of a lifetime, with hopes of this being his final job, his path collides with a disillusioned insurance broker who is facing her own crossroads. Determined to crack the case, a relentless detective closes in on the operation, raising the stakes even higher."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"크라임 101","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":135,"tagline":"Toujours prévoir sa sortie.","homepage":"","overview":"Un voleur insaisissable, dont les braquages spectaculaires mystifient la police. Lorsqu’il repère le coup du siècle, son chemin croise celui d’une courtière en assurances désabusée, elle-même à un tournant de sa vie. Convaincu qu’il tient une piste, un détective tenace se rapproche dangereusement de l’opération, faisant monter la tension d’un cran. À l’approche de ce braquage, la ligne entre chasseur et proie devient de plus en plus floue, et les trois protagonistes devront faire des choix cruciaux, tout en réalisant qu’il est désormais trop tard pour faire marche arrière."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"洛杉矶劫案","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"　　当多年来从未失手的珠宝大盗（克里斯·海姆斯沃斯 饰）决心干票大的就金盆洗手时，人生失意的保险公司高管（哈莉·贝瑞 饰）却意外加入，两人被迫联手。与此同时，一位警探（马克·鲁法洛 饰）正通过蛛丝马迹的线索将矛头对准他们。监守自盗的内鬼，黑吃黑的争斗，交错的阴谋下谁将成为这场惊天劫案的最终赢家？\r 　　影片改编自《纽约时报》榜首畅销书作者唐·温斯洛同名小说。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"犯罪101","runtime":0,"tagline":"100場精心策畫的劫案，1條退路。","homepage":"","overview":"一名神出鬼沒的大盜（克里斯漢斯沃飾）接連在加州經典地標，101號高速公路沿線完成多起驚天竊案，讓執法單位束手無策。就在他盯上一生一次的終極目標、企圖以此完成「最後一票」的同時，他的人生軌跡，意外與一名面臨人生轉折的失意保險經紀人（荷莉貝瑞飾）相撞，迫使兩人不得不聯手合作。\r 另一邊，執著破案、不肯放手的刑警（馬克魯法洛飾）緊追線索步步逼近，讓整場行動的風險與懸念持續升高。隨著這場價值數百萬美元的終極劫案即將展開，獵人與獵物之間的界線也逐漸模糊，三人都必須面對自己選擇的代價，因為此刻已經沒有回頭路。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Caminhos do Crime","runtime":0,"tagline":"Um assalto liga todos eles.","homepage":"","overview":"Um ladrão enigmático realiza assaltos de alto risco ao longo da icônica rodovia 101. Quando ele mira o golpe de sua vida — na esperança de que este seja seu último trabalho —, seu caminho cruza com o de uma corretora de seguros desiludida, forçando os dois a colaborar. Determinado a desvendar o caso, um detetive implacável se aproxima da operação."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"פשע 101","runtime":0,"tagline":"תמיד תשאירו דרך יציאה.","homepage":"","overview":"דייוויס הוא גנב מסתורי שמתמחה בשודים מסוכנים ביותר שמבלבלים את המשטרה פעם אחר פעם. הוא מתכנן את השוד הגדול ביותר בקריירה שלו ובתקווה שגם האחרון. הוא נאלץ לשתף פעולה עם שרון, מנהלת ביטוח מאוכזבת, ועם אורמן, גנב יריב בעל שיטות הרבה יותר אפלות.  ככל שמתקרב מועד השוד בשווי מיליוני דולרים, הבלש העקשן הסגן לובזניק סוגר עליהם, המתח גובר, ולא ברור יותר מי הצייד ומי הנרדף.  כל אחד מהם נאלץ להתמודד עם המחיר של הבחירות שלו ועם ההבנה שאין דרך חזרה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Tội Phạm 101","runtime":0,"tagline":"Một phi vụ kết nối tất cả.","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Crime 101 - La strada del crimine","runtime":0,"tagline":"Un gioco pericoloso li unisce tutti","homepage":"","overview":"Davis sta preparando il colpo più ambizioso della sua carriera, quello che spera sia l’ultimo, quando il destino lo porta a incrociare il cammino di Sharon, una cinica assicuratrice con cui è forzatamente costretto a collaborare, e di Orman, un pericoloso rivale con metodi ben più violenti. Mentre il furto multimilionario si avvicina, l’inarrestabile tenente Lubesnik stringe il cerchio, intensificando la tensione e assottigliando sempre più il confine tra cacciatore e preda. Ogni protagonista dovrà fare i conti con le conseguenze delle proprie scelte, consapevole di aver superato il punto di non ritorno."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"クライム101","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"アメリカ西海岸線を走るハイウェイ＜101＞号線で、数百万ドルの宝石が消える強盗事件が多発。４年間にも及ぶデーヴィスの犯行は一切のミスがなく完璧だったが、人生最大の大金を得るために高額商品を扱う保険会社に勤めるシャロンに接触し、共謀を持ちかけたことから思わぬ綻びを見せ始める──。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Ruta de escape","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Davis es un escurridizo ladrón cuyos atracos de alto riesgo tienen desconcertada a la policía. Davis está planeando su mayor golpe, con la esperanza de que sea el último, cuando se cruza en su camino Sharon, una desilusionada ejecutiva de seguros con la que se ve obligado a trabajar, y Orman un ladrón rival, con métodos mucho más inquietantes que los de Davis. A medida que se acerca el golpe multimillonario, el implacable teniente Lubesnik, se acerca a la operación, aumentando considerablemente el riesgo de lo que está en juego y difuminando la línea entre cazador y presa. Pronto, cada uno tendrá que aceptar el coste de sus decisiones asumiendo que no hay vuelta atrás."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Caminos del crimen","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un escurridizo ladrón ve la oportunidad de hacer el golpe de su vida con la esperanza de que sea su último trabajo. En su camino se cruza con una desilusionada corredora de seguros y también un implacable detective se acerca a la operación, lo que aumenta aún más lo que está en juego . A medida que se acerca el robo multimillonario, la línea entre cazador y presa comienza a difuminarse, y los tres se ven obligados a afrontar el coste de sus decisiones y darse cuenta de que no hay vuelta atrás."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Шлях до злочину","runtime":0,"tagline":"Одне пограбування об'єднає їх усіх","homepage":"","overview":"Під палючим сонцем Лос-Анджелеса «Шлях до злочину» розповідає історію невловимого грабіжника, який серією зухвалих пограбувань уздовж знаменитої траси 101 доводить поліцію до відчаю. Мріючи про останню й найризикованішу справу, він несподівано зустрічає на своєму шляху розчаровану життям страхову брокерку, яка й сама стоїть на порозі великих змін. Тим часом невтомний детектив крок за кроком наближається до розкриття злочинної схеми, а напруга зростає з кожним днем. Коли наближається мить великої афери, межа між мисливцем і здобиччю стирається, і всі троє змушені заплатити ціну за власні рішення — усвідомивши, що дороги назад більше немає."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Престъпление 101","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Когато неуловим крадец, чиито обири с високи залози се разгръщат по емблематичната магистрала 101 в Лос Анджелис, се стреми към резултата на живота си с надеждата това да бъде последната му работа, пътят му се пресича с разочарован застрахователен брокер, който се изправя пред собствения си кръстопът, принуждавайки ги да си сътрудничат. Решен да разкрие случая, безмилостен детектив се доближава до операцията, повишавайки залозите още повече. С наближаването на многомилионния обир границата между ловец и преследван започва да се размива, принуждавайки и тримата да се изправят пред цената на своите избори – и осъзнаването, че няма връщане назад."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Davis on arvoituksellinen varas, jonka korkean profiilin keikat ovat hämmentäneet poliisia. Hän suunnittelee elämänsä suurinta ryöstöä - toivoen sen olevan myös hänen viimeisensä - kun hänen tiensä risteää pettyneen vakuutusalan johtajan Sharonin kanssa. Pakotettuna työskentelemään Sharonin kanssa, on kuvioissa mukana myös kilpaileva varas Orman, jonka menetelmät ovat huomattavasti Davisia synkempiä. Kun monen miljonaan arvoinen ryöstö lähestyy, määrätietoinen etsivä Lubesnik kiristää otettaan operaatiosta, mikä nostaa panokset entisestään — ja metsästäjän ja saaliin välinen raja alkaa hämärtyä. Pian jokaisen on kohdattava tekojensa hinta — ja ymmärrettävä, ettei paluuta enää ole."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Ограбление в Лос-Анджелесе","runtime":0,"tagline":"«Все они связаны одним ограблением»","homepage":"https://www.sonypictures.co.uk/movies/crime-101","overview":"Детектив Лу Любник выслеживает похитителя драгоценностей и придерживается правил «Преступления 101» - строгого набора рекомендаций для идеального ограбления."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"A bűn útja","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A napsütötte, poros Los Angelesben játszódó Crime 101 egy titokzatos ékszertolvaj (Chris Hemsworth) történetét meséli el, aki a legendás 101-es autópálya mentén végrehajtott, milliós zsákmányú rablásaival hosszú ideje bolondot csinál a hatóságokból. Amikor végre az utolsó nagy dobására készül, amely után kiszállna, útja keresztezi egy kiégett biztosítási szakemberét (Halle Berry), aki maga is válaszút elé érkezett. A sors rákényszeríti őket az együttműködésre.  Időközben egy makacs és hajthatatlan nyomozó (Mark Ruffalo) egyre közelebb kerül az ügy megoldásához, ezzel tovább fokozva a feszültséget. Ahogy közeleg a többmillió dolláros rablás napja, a szerepek összemosódnak, és mindhárom szereplőnek szembe kell néznie tettei következményeivel, és azzal a felismeréssel, hogy már nincs visszaút.  (Gergo Horvath)"},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Autocesta zločina","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Kada se namjeri na plijen života, njegov se put ispreplete s razočaranom brokerskom agenticom osiguranja, koja se i sama nalazi na životnoj prekretnici. Uvjeren da je otkrio obrazac, neumoljivi detektiv sve mu je bliže, dodatno podižući uloge. Kako se velika pljačka približava, granica između lovca i lovine počinje se brisati, a svo troje suočavaju se s odlukama koje će im zauvijek promijeniti živote – i spoznajom da povratka više nema."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"เส้นทางปล้นโคตรระห่ำ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เรื่องราวของนักสืบ ลู ลูเบสนิก ที่กำลังตามรอยโจรขโมยเพชรคนหนึ่งที่ยึดมั่นในกฎ Crime 101 ซึ่งเป็นแนวทางปฏิบัติเคร่งครัดสำหรับการปล้นที่ไร้ที่ติ"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"დანაშაულის გზა","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"犯罪101","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"他策劃連環劫案，她選擇鋌而走險，他誓要成功破案⋯⋯一宗精心策劃的百萬珠寶劫案，三位陌生人的命運從此緊密糾纏！"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Ceļš uz noziegumu","runtime":135,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nenotverams zaglis, kurš cer uz savu pēdējo lielāko laupījumu, sastopas ar vīlušos apdrošinātāju, kura atrodas dzīves krustcelēs. Kad viņu ceļi krustojas, viņus sāk izsekot neatlaidīgs detektīvs, cerot izjaukt viņu plānoto multimiljonu dolāru laupījumu."},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":139,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Davis ist ein schwer fassbarer Juwelendieb, dessen Überfallserie die Polizei vor ein Rätsel stellt. Als er gerade den Coup seines Lebens ins Visier nimmt, trifft er auf die desillusionierte Versicherungsmanagerin Sharon, die selbst an einem Scheideweg steht. Überzeugt davon, ein Muster entdeckt zu haben, kommt währenddessen der unerbittliche Detective Lt. Lubesnik der ganzen Operation immer näher und erhöht damit das Risiko noch weiter."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Crime 101","runtime":139,"tagline":"Zawsze miej wyjście.","homepage":"","overview":"Crime 101 dzieje się w Los Angeles. To historia trzech nieznajomych, granych przez: Chrisa Hemswortha, Halle Berry i Marka Ruffalo, którzy znajdują się w punkcie zwrotnym swojego życia, a ich drogi krzyżują się, gdy ekscytujący i ryzykowny napad na wielomilionową sumę kusi ich obietnicą zmiany życia. W miarę jak stawka rośnie, bohaterowie są zmuszeni zmierzyć się z konsekwencjami swoich wyborów i uświadomić sobie, że nie ma już odwrotu."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":141,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Davis is een geraffineerde dief die met zijn gewaagde roofovervallen de politie voor een raadsel stelt. Tijdens de voorbereidingen op zijn grootste en hopelijk laatste klapper, kruist hij het pad van Sharon, een gedesillusioneerde topvrouw van een verzekeringmaatschappij. Hij wordt gedwongen om met haar samen te werken en met Orman, een rivaliserende dief die veel dubieuzere methoden hanteert dan Davis. Naarmate het moment van de miljoenenroof nadert, komt de onverzettelijke rechercheur Lubesnik het trio steeds dichter op de hielen te zitten, waardoor de spanning nog meer oploopt en het onderscheid tussen jager en prooi steeds meer begint te vervagen. Al gauw worden ze ieder voor zich geconfronteerd met de gevolgen van hun keuzes en met het besef dat er geen weg terug is."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"One heist connects them all","homepage":"","overview":"Davis är en slipad juveltjuv vars kupper har förbryllat polisen genom åren. När han planerar sin största stöt hittills, korsas hans väg av en desillusionerad försäkringsmäklare som själv står vid ett vägskäl. En envis polisutredare, övertygad om att han har hittat ett mönster, är dem hack i häl. När stöten närmar sig, börjar gränsen mellan jägare och jagad att suddas ut, och alla tre ställs inför livsavgörande val - och insikten att det inte finns någon väg tillbaka."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Ο Δρόμος του Εγκλήματος","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Με φόντο το ηλιόλουστο και την ίδια στιγμή σκοτεινό Λος Άντζελες, ένας μυστηριώδης ληστής κοσμημάτων έχει μπει στο στόχαστρο της αστυνομίας. Στο τελευταίο του μεγάλο κόλπο διασταυρώνεται με μια σύμβουλο ασφαλιστικής, που βρίσκεται και η ίδια σε ένα κρίσιμο σταυροδρόμι. Πεπεισμένος ότι έχει εντοπίσει ένα μοτίβο, ένας αμείλικτος ντετέκτιβ ακολουθεί τα ίχνη τους όλο και πιο κοντά. Καθώς η ληστεία πλησιάζει, τα όρια ανάμεσα στον κυνηγό και το θήραμα αρχίζουν να θολώνουν και οι τρεις ήρωες έρχονται αντιμέτωποι με επιλογές που θα καθορίσουν τη ζωή τους."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Autostrada crimei","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Plasat în Los Angeles, \"Autostrada crimei\" spune povestea unui hoț de bijuterii ale cărui jafuri au pus poliția în încurcătură. După ce pune ochii pe o pradă colosală, drumul lui se intersectează cu cel al unei agente de asigurări deziluzionate. Convins că a descoperit un tipar, un detectiv neobosit se apropie pe urmele hoțului. Pe măsură ce lovitura se apropie, linia dintre vânător și vânat începe să se estompeze, iar toți trei se confruntă cu alegeri decisive pentru viața lor și cu realizarea că nu mai există cale de întoarcere."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Cesta zločinu","runtime":0,"tagline":"Každá lúpež môže byť tá posledná","homepage":"","overview":"Chris Hemsworth sa v novom akčnom thrilleri predstaví ako Davis, nepolapiteľný zlodej šperkov stojaci pred najväčšou lúpežou svojho života. Do jeho života sa totiž nečakane pripletie poisťovacia maklérka Sharon, ktorej klienti patria medzi najbohatšiu elitu spoločnosti, čo Davis prirodzene musí využiť. Kým sa však pripravuje na dokonalú akciu, netuší, že po jeho stopách ide neúprosný detektív, odhodlaný legendárneho zlodeja chytiť za každú cenu. Hranica medzi lovcom a korisťou sa postupne stiera a Davis si začína uvedomovať, že tento kšeft môže byť jeho posledným..."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Bir hırsız ve bir sigorta acentesi, büyük bir soygun planlarken karşılaşırlar; bu sırada bir dedektif peşlerindedir."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":135,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Em “CRIME 101”, um moderno thriller policial repleto de reviravoltas, Davis (Chris Hemsworth) é um esquivo ladrão cujos assaltos de alto risco têm deixado a polícia intrigada. Enquanto planeia o maior golpe da sua vida — na esperança que seja o último — o seu caminho cruza-se com o de Sharon (Halle Berry), uma desiludida executiva de uma seguradora, com quem será forçado a trabalhar; e Orman (Barry Keoghan), um ladrão rival com métodos muito mais perturbadores do que os seus. À medida que o assalto de vários milhões de dólares se aproxima, o incansável detetive Tenente Lubesnik (Mark Ruffalo) aperta o cerco à operação, aumentando ainda mais a tensão e fazendo esbater a linha entre caçador e presa. Cada um deles é forçado a enfrentar o preço das suas próprias escolhas — e a perceber que já não há caminho de volta. “CRIME 101” é escrito e realizado por Bart Layton (“American Animals: O Assalto” e “The Imposter”)."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"699069cc38dbc6ffeaefab28","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/699069cc38dbc6ffeaefab28","author":"Manuel São Bento","content":"Full review: https://movieswetextedabout.com/crime-101-movie-review-chris-hemsworth-and-mark-ruffalo-anchor-a-heat-lite-crime-thriller/\r\n\r\nRating: B\r\n\r\n\"Crime 101 asserts itself as a solid and extremely competent crime thriller that, while not reaching the same thematic depths or cultural impact of the classics it's inspired by, offers high-level entertainment sustained by a luxury cast and irreproachable technical execution. By balancing the tension of expert editing with the humanity of its performances, Bart Layton delivers a movie that values the intelligence of viewers and the dignity of its characters. It's a film that celebrates the professionalism and persistence of the human spirit, reminding us that in a world plunged into chaos, there's a unique beauty in the precision of those who know the rules of the game and know when to follow or break them to do what's right.\"","created_at":"2026-02-14T12:25:48.186Z","updated_at":"2026-02-14T12:25:48.223Z","author_details":{"name":"Manuel São Bento","rating":7,"username":"msbreviews","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"6996e0ac58eabfd84e28943c","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6996e0ac58eabfd84e28943c","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$11","created_at":"2026-02-19T10:06:36.965Z","updated_at":"2026-02-19T10:11:08.225Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":6,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}},{"id":"699a65189c3ae3e3ce0e4d0a","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/699a65189c3ae3e3ce0e4d0a","author":"MovieGuys","content":"The aptly named \"Crime 101\" looks a lot like any by the numbers entry-level script for an action crime drama/thriller. \r\n\r\nThere's exactly nothing new on offer here. Unless you are 100% new to the genre, this film will feel overly familiar, tired, predictable and ultimately clichéd. Dropping in a cast of well-known faces does nothing to fix the lack of originality on offer here.\r\n\r\nI managed a little over half of this flick before remembering I only had one life and didn't want to waste it watching the same thing over and over again, ad nauseum. \r\n\r\nIn summary, in spite of decent production values and a more or less capable cast (there's at least one actor here I don't rate), this is a rather unoriginal film that shows little to no imagination, as far as I can see. A mediocre watch.","created_at":"2026-02-22T02:08:24.793Z","updated_at":"2026-02-22T22:42:48.709Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":6,"username":"MovieGuys","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"699a65ece622d15634e8f064","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/699a65ece622d15634e8f064","author":"Brent Marchant","content":"$12","created_at":"2026-02-22T02:11:56.526Z","updated_at":"2026-02-22T02:11:56.546Z","author_details":{"name":"Brent Marchant","rating":7,"username":"Brent_Marchant","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[],"similar_content":[{"id":59,"adult":false,"title":"A History of Violence","video":false,"overview":"An average family is thrust into the spotlight after the father commits a seemingly self-defense murder at his diner.","genre_ids":[18,53,80],"popularity":2.9401,"vote_count":3617,"poster_path":"/3qnO72NHmUgs9JZXAmu4aId9QDl.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-23","vote_average":7.164,"backdrop_path":"/iZHJsUYxhjI6kbooHoQRWXv6F8E.jpg","original_title":"A History of Violence","original_language":"en"},{"id":66,"adult":false,"title":"Absolute Power","video":false,"overview":"A master thief coincidentally is robbing a house where a murder—in which the President of the United States is involved—occurs in front of his eyes. He is forced to run, while holding evidence that could convict the President.","genre_ids":[80,18,28],"popularity":2.2658,"vote_count":1203,"poster_path":"/izvyt3cxlilhbYwybTOteDWqf99.jpg","release_date":"1997-02-14","vote_average":6.658,"backdrop_path":"/cLftTzGw40BlLw8IggKSWDjKOQo.jpg","original_title":"Absolute Power","original_language":"en"},{"id":74,"adult":false,"title":"War of the Worlds","video":false,"overview":"Ray Ferrier is a divorced dockworker and less-than-perfect father. Soon after his ex-wife and her new husband drop off his teenage son and young daughter for a rare weekend visit, a strange and powerful lightning storm touches down.","genre_ids":[12,53,878],"popularity":9.6095,"vote_count":8978,"poster_path":"/6Biy7R9LfumYshur3YKhpj56MpB.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-28","vote_average":6.531,"backdrop_path":"/bInicBgSHfQiWLbnRT5jxw9Grvm.jpg","original_title":"War of the Worlds","original_language":"en"},{"id":77,"adult":false,"title":"Memento","video":false,"overview":"Leonard Shelby is tracking down the man who raped and murdered his wife. The difficulty of locating his wife's killer, however, is compounded by the fact that he suffers from a rare, untreatable form of short-term memory loss. Although he can recall details of life before his accident, Leonard cannot remember what happened fifteen minutes ago, where he's going, or why.","genre_ids":[9648,53],"popularity":9.0867,"vote_count":15929,"poster_path":"/fKTPH2WvH8nHTXeBYBVhawtRqtR.jpg","release_date":"2000-10-11","vote_average":8.176,"backdrop_path":"/7Wev9JMo6R5XAfz2KDvXb7oPMmy.jpg","original_title":"Memento","original_language":"en"},{"id":78,"adult":false,"title":"Blade Runner","video":false,"overview":"In the smog-choked dystopian Los Angeles of 2019, blade runner Rick Deckard is called out of retirement to terminate a quartet of replicants who have escaped to Earth seeking their creator for a way to extend their short life spans.","genre_ids":[878,18,53],"popularity":12.05,"vote_count":14715,"poster_path":"/63N9uy8nd9j7Eog2axPQ8lbr3Wj.jpg","release_date":"1982-06-25","vote_average":7.94,"backdrop_path":"/hJ5R9d6QuH3tzr8L8neZZTuzNXm.jpg","original_title":"Blade Runner","original_language":"en"},{"id":82,"adult":false,"title":"Miami Vice","video":false,"overview":"A case involving drug lords and murder in South Florida takes a personal turn for undercover detectives Sonny Crockett and Ricardo Tubbs. Unorthodox Crockett gets involved romantically with the Chinese-Cuban wife of a trafficker of arms and drugs, while Tubbs deals with an assault on those he loves.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"popularity":2.8188,"vote_count":1916,"poster_path":"/1KGD2g0wOc7WBfHc5G19reLHQxk.jpg","release_date":"2006-07-27","vote_average":6.022,"backdrop_path":"/lV2UQv1qmiZA0tWsVjgFLD6z2uG.jpg","original_title":"Miami Vice","original_language":"en"},{"id":96,"adult":false,"title":"Beverly Hills Cop II","video":false,"overview":"Axel Foley returns to the land of sunshine and palm trees to investigate the near-fatal shooting of police Captain Andrew Bogomil. With the help of Sgt. Taggart and Det. Rosewood, they soon uncover that the shooting is associated with a series of \"alphabet\" robberies masterminded by a heartless weapons kingpin—and the chase is on.","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"popularity":4.3923,"vote_count":2756,"poster_path":"/egDakU8O5yUwpUJP9IMAUVtIDll.jpg","release_date":"1987-05-18","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/bIA65PCRtIQfBvIoKohJbtOPl3M.jpg","original_title":"Beverly Hills Cop II","original_language":"en"},{"id":134,"adult":false,"title":"O Brother, Where Art Thou?","video":false,"overview":"In the deep south during the 1930s, three escaped convicts search for hidden treasure while a relentless lawman pursues them.","genre_ids":[12,35,80],"popularity":5.3967,"vote_count":4492,"poster_path":"/s9foMAcLg8GEzzQzer04qOGdD1k.jpg","release_date":"2000-08-30","vote_average":7.321,"backdrop_path":"/rbsm633lnt3hKHEpk7FOt3dy82a.jpg","original_title":"O Brother, Where Art Thou?","original_language":"en"},{"id":204,"adult":false,"title":"The Wages of Fear","video":false,"overview":"In a run-down South American town, four men are paid to drive trucks loaded with nitroglycerin into the jungle through to the oil field. Friendships are tested and rivalries develop as they embark upon the perilous journey.","genre_ids":[18,53,12],"popularity":1.9299,"vote_count":1053,"poster_path":"/sNOvIp4X0fmCMfgEs2ww5IyMgFm.jpg","release_date":"1953-04-22","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/hTP6H7sNlWXdGxAciXQSjNJ1ob7.jpg","original_title":"Le Salaire de la peur","original_language":"fr"},{"id":218,"adult":false,"title":"The Terminator","video":false,"overview":"In the post-apocalyptic future, reigning tyrannical supercomputers teleport a cyborg assassin known as the \"Terminator\" back to 1984 to kill Sarah Connor, whose unborn son is destined to lead insurgents against 21st century mechanical hegemony. Meanwhile, the human-resistance movement dispatches a lone warrior to safeguard Sarah. Can he stop the virtually indestructible killing machine?","genre_ids":[28,53,878],"popularity":17.7814,"vote_count":14311,"poster_path":"/qvktm0BHcnmDpul4Hz01GIazWPr.jpg","release_date":"1984-10-26","vote_average":7.675,"backdrop_path":"/ffdqHMWkh1h9MABwIfbfRJhgFW6.jpg","original_title":"The Terminator","original_language":"en"},{"id":247,"adult":false,"title":"The Killing","video":false,"overview":"Career criminal Johnny Clay recruits a sharpshooter, a crooked police officer, a bartender and a betting teller named George, among others, for one last job before he goes straight and gets married. But when George tells his restless wife about the scheme to steal millions from the racetrack where he works, she hatches a plot of her own.","genre_ids":[80,53],"popularity":1.7449,"vote_count":1680,"poster_path":"/A6VzUPcADZGYdGHlVdWvpMNDF5d.jpg","release_date":"1956-06-06","vote_average":7.646,"backdrop_path":"/2EltoldCMsYmP2BXJVGiuNalEWv.jpg","original_title":"The Killing","original_language":"en"},{"id":250,"adult":false,"title":"In China They Eat Dogs","video":false,"overview":"Arvid is an ordinary bank clerk who lives a rather unassuming life with his dear girlfriend. But his life is turned completely upside down when he bravely manages to avert a robbery against the bank where he works.","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"popularity":0.9502,"vote_count":287,"poster_path":"/v78NxEyzsElWnwSvGWpvf2DCzP9.jpg","release_date":"1999-09-10","vote_average":7.347,"backdrop_path":"/bZt4CwuaZWadSh9OEcNQCZbPFR1.jpg","original_title":"I Kina spiser de hunde","original_language":"da"},{"id":253,"adult":false,"title":"Live and Let Die","video":false,"overview":"James Bond must investigate a mysterious murder case of a British agent in New Orleans. Soon he finds himself up against a gangster boss named Mr. Big.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":3.8501,"vote_count":2226,"poster_path":"/39qkrjqMZs6utwNmihVImC3ghas.jpg","release_date":"1973-06-27","vote_average":6.509,"backdrop_path":"/hzmmXx6UeYQeylioNbliFKjSbV7.jpg","original_title":"Live and Let Die","original_language":"en"},{"id":257,"adult":false,"title":"Oliver Twist","video":false,"overview":"When 9-year-old orphan Oliver Twist dares to ask his cruel taskmaster, Mr. Bumble, for a second serving of gruel, he's hired out as an apprentice. Escaping that dismal fate, young Oliver falls in with the street urchin known as the Artful Dodger and his criminal mentor, Fagin. When kindly Mr. Brownlow takes Oliver in, Fagin's evil henchman Bill Sikes plots to kidnap the boy.","genre_ids":[80,18,10751],"popularity":2.0641,"vote_count":1226,"poster_path":"/zhPdYZ3x2uanhM1SyBj4CuL6hSa.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-23","vote_average":6.747,"backdrop_path":"/s4H3XiCwHrjtMP4cBCO5L5tDVg3.jpg","original_title":"Oliver Twist","original_language":"en"},{"id":260,"adult":false,"title":"The 39 Steps","video":false,"overview":"Richard Hanney has a rude awakening when a glamorous female spy falls into his bed - with a knife in her back. Having a bit of trouble explaining it all to Scotland Yard, he heads for the hills of Scotland to try to clear his name by locating the spy ring known as The 39 Steps.","genre_ids":[9648,53],"popularity":1.4981,"vote_count":1030,"poster_path":"/oC81jK6aAug4MA0xzYVngHmjsZS.jpg","release_date":"1935-06-06","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/zqLR4jm0lPFGnyN55QBSf4pzz5n.jpg","original_title":"The 39 Steps","original_language":"en"},{"id":90,"adult":false,"title":"Beverly Hills Cop","video":false,"overview":"Fast-talking, quick-thinking Detroit street cop Axel Foley has bent more than a few rules and regs in his time, but when his best friend is murdered, he heads to sunny Beverly Hills to work the case like only he can.","genre_ids":[35,80,28],"popularity":5.0915,"vote_count":4498,"poster_path":"/eBJEvKkhQ0tUt1dBAcTEYW6kCle.jpg","release_date":"1984-12-05","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/tKi5HYDSuxP4I26fxyF2UVvAtLa.jpg","original_title":"Beverly Hills Cop","original_language":"en"},{"id":93,"adult":false,"title":"Anatomy of a Murder","video":false,"overview":"Semi-retired Michigan lawyer Paul Biegler takes the case of Army Lt. Manion, who murdered a local innkeeper after his wife claimed that he raped her. Over the course of an extensive trial, Biegler parries with District Attorney Lodwick and out-of-town prosecutor Claude Dancer to set his client free, but his case rests on the victim's mysterious business partner, who's hiding a dark secret.","genre_ids":[80,18,9648],"popularity":1.6093,"vote_count":1126,"poster_path":"/b2G1QSAwtBv9luhEwErIgSRaU92.jpg","release_date":"1959-07-01","vote_average":7.835,"backdrop_path":"/xfEU7DOlQPwz8Y0TBhKmpETuNIc.jpg","original_title":"Anatomy of a Murder","original_language":"en"},{"id":107,"adult":false,"title":"Snatch","video":false,"overview":"Unscrupulous boxing promoters, violent bookies, a Russian gangster, incompetent amateur robbers, and supposedly Jewish jewellers fight to track down a priceless stolen diamond.","genre_ids":[80,35],"popularity":8.4587,"vote_count":9772,"poster_path":"/kJZoAHq1SLDdWjeNGtlHAnGpmFV.jpg","release_date":"2000-09-01","vote_average":7.816,"backdrop_path":"/gTghF8ardwJ48XLHkiapWk3ZmSo.jpg","original_title":"Snatch","original_language":"en"},{"id":115,"adult":false,"title":"The Big Lebowski","video":false,"overview":"Jeffrey 'The Dude' Lebowski, a Los Angeles slacker who only wants to bowl and drink White Russians, is mistaken for another Jeffrey Lebowski, a wheelchair-bound millionaire, and finds himself dragged into a strange series of events involving nihilists, adult film producers, ferrets, errant toes, and large sums of money.","genre_ids":[35,80],"popularity":8.0204,"vote_count":11962,"poster_path":"/9mprbw31MGdd66LR0AQKoDMoFRv.jpg","release_date":"1998-03-06","vote_average":7.839,"backdrop_path":"/hXsy4XCCHrUk81XoRhcooyWejao.jpg","original_title":"The Big Lebowski","original_language":"en"},{"id":274,"adult":false,"title":"The Silence of the Lambs","video":false,"overview":"Clarice Starling is a top student at the FBI's training academy.  Jack Crawford wants Clarice to interview Dr. Hannibal Lecter, a brilliant psychiatrist who is also a violent psychopath, serving life behind bars for various acts of murder and cannibalism.  Crawford believes that Lecter may have insight into a case and that Starling, as an attractive young woman, may be just the bait to draw him out.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"popularity":3.7028,"vote_count":17611,"poster_path":"/uS9m8OBk1A8eM9I042bx8XXpqAq.jpg","release_date":"1991-02-14","vote_average":8.346,"backdrop_path":"/aYcnDyLMnpKce1FOYUpZrXtgUye.jpg","original_title":"The Silence of the Lambs","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt32430579","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":"Crime101Film","wikidata_id":"Q126394034","instagram_id":"crime101film"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":"Crime101Film","instagram":"crime101film"},"gdvg_id":148744,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AM","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2026-02-12T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"AR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2026-02-12T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"+13"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"AT","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2026-02-13T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"AU","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2026-02-12T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"M"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"AZ","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors